>>PUBLICATIONS
    1.ID
    2.NAME
    3.BOOKS[]

>>>>>>>>>>API'S<<<<<<<<<<<<<<<
_________________________________________________________________________________________________________
>>BOOKS
    METHOD: get
        to get all the BOOKS 
        to get a specific based on the ISBN
        to get a list of books based on the CATEGORY[]
        to get a list of books based on the AUTHORS[]   >>>pending.....
   
    METHOD: post --> add
        New Book
   
    METHOD: put -->update
        update book details
        update or add new author    >>>>>>>pending

    METHOD: delete
        delete a book
        delete an author from a book
_________________________________________________________________________________________________________
>>AUTHORS
    METHOD: get
        To get all the AUTHORS
        To get the specific author
        to get a list of author based on a book
   
    METHOD: post
        New Author
    METHOD: put 
        update author name using id >>>>>pending

    METHOD: delete
        delete Author
_________________________________________________________________________________________________________
>>PUBLICATIONS
    METHOD: GET 
        To get all the PUBLICATIONS
        To get a specific AUTHOR 
        To get a list of specific PUBLICATIONS based on the book
   
    METHOD: post
        add New PUBLICATIONS

    METHOD: put >>>>>>pending
        update PUBLICATIONs name using id
        update or add new book to a PUBLICATIONS

    METHOD: delete
        delete a PUBLICATIONS
        delete a book from PUBLICATIONS
